row.Note2: Most of the Grant files pertain to a particular grants made by CCNY and are filed in alphabetical order by the names of the institutions and individuals to which CCNY made grants. This subseries includes files for grants made to establish tasks forces, and commissions, and councils that were administered by Corporation staff. While a large majority of the material dates from 1911-1988, there are documents within the grant files from before and after these dates. Until 1983, grant reports too large to be kept in the original grant file were shelved separately. These reports are listed in suberies B.
